                            <comment id="15034504" author="jahewson" created="Tue, 1 Dec 2015 20:18:38 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;If you can&apos;t read from the filesystem, why are you using FileSystemFontProvider?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15034509" author="ssteiner1" created="Tue, 1 Dec 2015 20:26:15 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I&apos;m using the default, normally things will be skipped rather than failing when they cant access disk&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
